isis.stitle: TSI 04-12-14 - Performance Specifications for Model Year 2002 and 2003 International® VT 365 Engine Applications

subjectgroup.subject: Performance Specifications for Model Year 2002 and 2003 International® VT 365 Engine Applications

geninfo.para:
Model Year 2003
and updated Model Year 2002
performance specifications for the International® VT 365 are released for service. Discard and replace TSI-02-12-24 with this TSI and file in Appendix A of diagnostic manual EGES-240.
